      • canCreateNeutronLoadBalancerPoolMember

        int canCreateNeutronLoadBalancerPoolMember(NeutronLoadBalancerPoolMember loadBalancerPoolMember)
        Services provide this interface method to indicate if the specified loadBalancerPoolMember can be created
        Parameters:
        loadBalancerPoolMember - instance of proposed new LoadBalancerPool object
        Returns:
        integer the return value is understood to be a HTTP status code. A return value outside of 200 through 299 results in the create operation being interrupted and the returned status value reflected in the HTTP response.

      • canUpdateNeutronLoadBalancerPoolMember

        int canUpdateNeutronLoadBalancerPoolMember(NeutronLoadBalancerPoolMember delta,
                                         NeutronLoadBalancerPoolMember original)
        Services provide this interface method to indicate if the specified loadBalancerPoolMember can be changed using the specified delta
        Parameters:
        delta - updates to the loadBalancerPoolMember object using patch semantics
        original - instance of the LoadBalancerPool object to be updated
        Returns:
        integer the return value is understood to be a HTTP status code. A return value outside of 200 through 299 results in the update operation being interrupted and the returned status value reflected in the HTTP response.
